Subject: CaaB In Person Meeting- Nationals Team [In-person]
BodyText:
Hi Team,

We have a new vendor to the Strategic Procurement Team that will be in June 3rd. This vendor sells Cloud Infrastructure as a service. Their competitors are AWS, GCP, Azure and Digital Ocean. https://caab.cloud/

Feel free to stop by to meet the CaaB reps and hear more about the solution.
